{"tid":2136720,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"真想不到當初我們也討厭阿迪達","createTime":"2020-08-02T10:58:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-02T16:31:54.000Z","uid":136116,"like":11,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"8ca0991eb8bc2ebd3c07b3dbfe404999bfb330a6","tid":2136720,"uid":136116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T10:58:32.000Z","msg":"共你捧杯再舉箸 <br />\n突然間相看莞爾 <br />\n場中透著那味兒 <br />\n大概足總有些事 <br />\n是迷轟都不可以 <br />\n明白其妙處  <br />\n<br />\n就像你當日痛心愛蛇敗北多介意<br />\n怎發現你從雲格亦能學懂開解與寬恕 <br />\n也像我很糾結的轟子 <br />\n此際回頭看 原來並沒有事  <br />\n<em><span class=\"green\">更多更詳盡歌詞 在 ※ <a href=\"http://Mojim.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FMojim.com&d=aFheyUS8Hi5o9a%2F4VMBAnY6aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=e4103d27\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Mojim.com</a>　魔鏡歌詞網 </span></em><br />\n<br />\n真想不到當初我們也討厭阿迪達 <br />\n今天竟吃得出那達蛇愈來愈記掛 <br />\n開始時捱一些苦 <br />\n栽種絕處歐霸<br />\n幸得艱辛的引路捧杯不致太寡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5228c3c59b6c7b3e5d369eff87f1752a44a2183","tid":2136720,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T10:58:50.000Z","msg":"波台手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bf38da6f1eb9b639fbeeb45f0088fea073f01f1","tid":2136720,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T10:59:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4427d4040fe3721f2b154342de1818b1391cf397","tid":2136720,"uid":66839,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T10:59:08.000Z","msg":"完全唔岩音"},{"pid":"b5f73a5fef68cd8af4fef8bffd639d8dabf2b4cd","tid":2136720,"uid":241543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T10:59:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"819ef0d768cab60ce5f351a6790a56fe5a48f766","tid":2136720,"uid":136116,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4427d4040fe3